# Examples

## Basic Usage

### Using the Function

```python
from {{ project_name | snake_case | replace('-', '_') }} import example_function

# Simple usage
result = example_function("hello world")
print(result)
# {'input': 'hello world', 'processed': True, 'options': {}}

# With options
result = example_function(
    {"key": "value"},
    options={"debug": True}
)
print(result)
```

### Using the Class

```python
from {{ project_name | snake_case | replace('-', '_') }} import ExampleClass

# Create instance
processor = ExampleClass("my-processor")

# Process data
result = processor.process({"data": "test"})
print(result)
# {'name': 'my-processor', 'data': {'data': 'test'}}
```

