## Async Usage

```python
import asyncio
from {{ project_name | snake_case | replace('-', '_') }} import ExampleClass

async def main():
    processor = ExampleClass("async-processor")
    result = await processor.process_async({"data": "test"})
    print(result)

asyncio.run(main())
```
